      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "True Hunters",
        "Client": "Admiral Galleus",
        "Description": "The Fierce, and the renowned hero\r\nand hunter Elder Fugen. We are\r\nmost fortunate to have allies such\r\nas yourselves! I\u0027d like to further\r\nstrengthen our bond with a hunt!\r\nMay the alliance between Kamura\r\nand the Kingdom be everlasting!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Seregios\r\nand slay a Shagaru Magala",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Les vrais chasseurs",
        "Client": "Amiral Galleus",
        "Description": "La Flamme, et le c\u00E9l\u00E8bre h\u00E9ros\r\net chasseur, Fugen l\u0027Ancien,\r\nje veux tout savoir sur vous\r\ndeux. Mais une chasse vaut\r\nmieux que n\u0027importe quel\r\ndiscours \u00E0 mes yeux, alors\r\nqu\u0027attendons-nous ?",
        "Target": "Chasser un Seregios et\r\ntuer un Shagaru Magala",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Veri cacciatori",
        "Client": "Ammiraglio Galleus",
        "Description": "Audace e Fugen l\u0027anziano,\r\neroe e leggenda di Kamura.\r\nVoglio imparare a conoscervi\r\nmeglio ma, essendo cacciatori,\r\nuna caccia vale pi\u00F9 di mille\r\nparole. Che la conversazione\r\nabbia inizio!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Seregios\r\ne uccidi un Shagaru Magala",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Wahre J\u00E4ger",
        "Client": "Galleus",
        "Description": "\u003CLSNR {Der Grimmige} {Die Grimmige}\u003E und der ber\u00FChmte\r\nHeld Fogen. Ich m\u00F6chte unser\r\nB\u00FCndnis mit einer Jagd st\u00E4rken!\r\nM\u00F6ge die Allianz zwischen\r\nKamura und dem K\u00F6nigreich\r\newig w\u00E4hren!",
